  "keyFeatures": [
    "Simple API for 2D game development in Go",
    "Cross-platform: Windows, macOS, Linux, iOS, Android, WebAssembly",
    "Hardware-accelerated rendering via OpenGL/Metal/DirectX",
    "Built-in audio playback support",
    "Custom shader support via Kage shading language",
    "Gamepad and touch input handling",
    "Image/sprite management and drawing primitives",
    "Go module support with no CGo dependencies on most platforms"
